data.description: NEW PRICE & BUYER INCENTIVES! Stunning move in ready 3 BD, 2.5 BA home offers everything for a seamless buyer move in.  Located in Desirable Franklin Meadows Subdivision, this home is eligible for 1% buyer incentives to lower interest rate to save you hundreds a month on your mortgage or help pay buyers closing cost!   Newer paint throughout this open concept home! Open kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, granite counters and plenty of cabinet space.  Huge bonus room over the garage for extra entertainment / living area with plenty of storage throughout home.  Spacious master bedroom comes with large closets and huge tub with stand up shower & double vanities in bathroom.  Home also offers huge fenced in backyard with plenty of privacy on your deck that is great for entertaining and cookouts.
